<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Troubleshooting Guide</title>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@1.9.0"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Troubleshooting Guide</h1>
    
    <p>Common errors and how to resolve them.</p>
    
    <h2>HTTP Error Codes</h2>
    
    <p>Reference table for all possible HTTP error responses:</p>
    
    <img src="../images/error-codes.gif" alt="HTTP Error Codes Reference">
    
    <h2>Common Issues</h2>
    
    <div hx-get="/api/status" hx-trigger="load">
        <h3>401 Unauthorized</h3>
        <p>This error occurs when:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>No Authorization header provided</li>
            <li>JWT token is expired</li>
            <li>Token signature is invalid</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Re-authenticate and obtain a new token.</p>
        
        <h3>403 Forbidden</h3>
        <p>User is authenticated but lacks permission for the resource.</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Contact administrator for proper role assignment.</p>
        
        <h3>429 Too Many Requests</h3>
        <p>Rate limit has been exceeded.</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Wait for the rate limit window to reset (typically 60 seconds).</p>
        
        <h3>500 Internal Server Error</h3>
        <p>Unexpected server condition. Check server logs for details.</p>
        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Report to development team with request ID from response headers.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
